summary: Human Resources/Office Manager with 4 years of experience in employee management, hiring, computer training and benefits. Detail-oriented, organized, and results-driven with strong communication, analytical and data-entry skills. Experienced in payroll, scheduling, training, and customer service.

experience.title: Office Manager
experience.description: Managed front office operations; data entry and records maintenance; handled payments (VA, MYCAA, DARS); assisted CNA instructor; recruited and interviewed applicants; managed I-9/W-2; conducted new employee orientation; advised managers on policy matters; supported programs to maximize customer satisfaction.

experience.title: Leasing Specialist
experience.description: Collaborated with operations for rental inventory; prepared leasing reports; greeted prospective residents; conducted background/credit checks; managed money and bank procedures; facilitated move-ins; performed bank/corporate audits.

experience.title: Administrative Assistant/Office Manager
experience.description: Managed purchasing, hiring, terminations and travel logistics; bi-weekly payroll via ADP; coordinated reporting, acquisitions, leases and sales; screened candidates and conducted interviews; maintained Excel spreadsheets.

experience.title: Barista/Office Manager
experience.description: Managed 6 employees; payroll via ADP; bank deposits; sales and marketing; opening/closing the stand; scheduling; training new hires; maintained sales-tracking spreadsheets.

experience.title: Retail Apparel Associate
experience.description: Cashier; merchandising; stock room to sales floor; daily customer service; opened/closed store; stock and fitting room oversight.
